title: Amy’s Son Got In Trouble + Eddie's Coronavirus News + Bobby’s Mailbag: Neighbor’s Nanny Flirting With Husband
itunes:title: Amy’s Son Got In Trouble + Eddie's Coronavirus News + Bobby’s Mailbag: Neighbor’s Nanny Flirting With Husband
description:
Amy’s son got in trouble at tutoring for something he said. Amy admits that he may have learned it from her. We check in with Eddie who gives us some GOOD news and BAD news on the possibility of him having coronavirus. Plus, we open up the mailbag from a listener who has an issue with her neighbor’s nanny!
